OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLabour MP calls for duty of
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcare for abuse survivors   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Labour MP Apsana Begum has called for a
OL,6, duty of care to be placed on political 
OL,7, parties and employers to ensure that   
OL,8, survivors of domestic abuse are not    
OL,9, exposed to further harassment.         
OL,11,FMs Begum told MPs she had been in a    
OL,12,Fmarriage to a man which had become     
OL,13,F"volatile and abusive".                
OL,15,FSpeaking in a Westminster Hall debate, 
OL,16,Fshe claimed he had continued to harass 
OL,17,Fher after the relationship ended.      
OL,19,FBut her ex-husband accused her of using
OL,20,F"a false narrative of domestic abuse". 
